# DisasterSAS — Full System Walkthrough

Complete Disaster Management System with Flask backend and HTML/CSS/JS frontend covering all 9 modules.

## System Architecture

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph Frontend["Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS)"]
        LOGIN[Login / Register]
        DASH[Dashboard]
        WEATHER[Weather Monitor]
        MAP[Live Map]
        ALERTS[Alerts]
        SHELTERS[Shelters]
        SURVIVORS[Survivors]
        MISSING[Missing Persons]
        VOLUNTEERS[Volunteers]
        REQUESTS[Emergency Requests]
        RESOURCES[Resources]
        EMERGENCY[Emergency Contacts]
    end
    
    subgraph Backend["Flask Backend"]
        API[REST APIs]
        SOCKET[Socket.IO]
        EMAIL[Email Service]
    end
    
    subgraph Database["SQLite Database"]
        MODELS["10 Models"]
    end
    
    Frontend --> API
    API --> Database
    SOCKET --> Frontend
    API --> EMAIL
```

## Modules Implemented

| # | Module | Backend | Frontend | Key Features |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| 1 | Weather Monitoring | [weather.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/weather.py) | [weather.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/weather.html) | Real-time API, disaster detection, auto-alerts, email notifications |
| 2 | Shelter Management | [shelter_routes.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/shelter_routes.py) | [shelters.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/shelters.html) | CRUD, nearest shelter (Haversine), capacity tracking, stats |
| 3 | Volunteer Management | [volunteer_routes.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/volunteer_routes.py) | [volunteers.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/volunteers.html) | Skill categories, shelter assignment, volunteer limits |
| 4 | Survivor Registration | [survivor_routes.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/survivor_routes.py) | [survivors.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/survivors.html) | Auto-updates shelter occupancy, search across shelters |
| 5 | Missing Person Tracking | [missing_routes.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/missing_routes.py) | [missing.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/missing.html) | Report, search, mark as found |
| 6 | Emergency Requests | [request_routes.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/request_routes.py) | [requests.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/requests.html) | Food/water/medical/evacuation, status workflow |
| 7 | Resource Management | [resource_routes.py](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disaster_backend/routes/resource_routes.py) | [resources.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/resources.html) | Per-shelter inventory, low-stock alerts |
| 8 | Dashboard | `dashboard/stats` | [dashboard.html](file:///d:/DisasterSAS/disater_frontend/dashboard.html) | All module stats, 2 charts, recent alerts |
| 9 | Notifications | Socket.IO + email | Toast system | Real-time alerts, email on disaster detection |

